  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9IVkJJRkxMLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/HVBIFLL.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HVBIFLL.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HVBIFLL.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mcEw5dFZRLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/fpL9tVQ.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fpL9tVQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fpL9tVQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8zZVh3TE1kLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eXwLMd.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eXwLMd.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eXwLMd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9WdDZpSmdvLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vt6iJgo.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vt6iJgo.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vt6iJgo.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n聪慧西施遁江湖<br/>\r\n玉腕自断虞姬舞<br/>\r\n千年后也余雍容<br/>\r\n里外通吃曰爱国。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n习大马棒骄横倨傲叉坐酒席前<br/>\r\n身后阉宦太监捧着主子影型舔<br/>\r\n左右拥围法兰西纯的杂的来宾<br/>\r\n酒池肉林极尽奢华飘鬓香姿倩<br/>\r\n觥筹交错推杯换盏皆笑语盈盈<br/>\r\n辉映些阮晓寰妻子哭上诉无门<br/>\r\n胡鑫宇妈妈撕心裂肺反复昏厥<br/>\r\n还记得举白纸大学生李康梦们<br/>\r\n张家界跳崖飞渡绝望送命青春<br/>\r\n这对照分明这天端地界太差别<br/>\r\n远非那辞官归故漏夜赶考戏谑<br/>\r\n糟蹋香港恫吓台湾恶助俄攻乌<br/>\r\n杀惯同胞便哄万邦来朝宰世界<br/>\r\n血沾的茅台骨垫的烹饪邀夷蛮<br/>\r\n开怀的畅饮蠕动的肥脸品尝鲜<br/>\r\n广州深圳失业的中年流浪车站<br/>\r\n郑州西安烂尾楼摇曳烛火难眠<br/>\r\n哦这对照分明天端地界太差别！<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/id-56834__sort_key-agree_count__sort-DESC\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/id-56834__sort_key-agree_count__sort-DESC\">启发篇：观巩俐随马克龙访华深夜有感</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57177\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57177\">法共主席兼总统访华</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\"><b>匪域笑林</b></a> </div>",
